#(c) 2013 Sam Caldwell.  All Rights Reserved.
#
# The /srv/nemesis/web/ subtree contains static web content (HTML).
# This content includes the static pages for each server as well as
# statistics data.
#
# Static content may include HTML redirects and JavaScript-based pages.
#
# Statistics data includes HTML files created by server cron jobs, etc.
# in order to report each server's state.
#
# ---TREE---
#
# 	/srv
#	  |
#	  +--->/nemesis
#			   |
#              +---->/web
#					   |
#				       +--->/SERVER_TYPE
#								|
#								+--->/static
#								|
#								+--->/stats
#
#